Subject: [PATCH 04/10] panfrost: Add FS clip distance prolog NIR builder

Build a standalone fragment shader prolog that loads clip distances
from individual VAR slots with perspective-correct interpolation,
multiplies by FragCoord.w to recover linear interpolation, and
discards fragments where any clip distance is negative.

This is compiled independently and concatenated with the main FS
via pan_fast_link() at draw time.

